    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that looks great on the road. It\u2019s been well-loved and carefully maintained, so it's totally ready for your next big road trip or just the daily commute. I\u2019ve truly enjoyed every mile in it, and I\u2019m sure you will too! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
