      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) represents a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing, providing immediate throttle response and a screaming 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory-limited slip differential, ensuring maximum traction through the corners. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed suspension setup featuring Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows honest signs of use, the mechanical vitals are robust, with recent valve adjustments and cooling system overhauls completed. A true driver's spec for those who prioritize analog feedback and peak longitudinal performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Minimal wear. Runs well.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch, consistent with careful use. The factory alloy wheels are free of major curb rash and are fitted with high-quality tires showing approximately 70% tread life. Inside, the interior is clean and smoke-free. The leather upholstery is in excellent shape, with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features, including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and a fresh multi-point inspection. The engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the suspension remains firm and quiet over bumps. Included are all service records from my ownership, the original owner\u2019s manual, and two key fobs. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, a testament to quality engineering and consistent care. This model offers a refined driving experience, characterized by mechanical reliability and a well-preserved interior. Thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our high standards for performance and safety, this vehicle represents an ideal acquisition for those who prioritize both value and long-term dependability. Experience the assurance of a vehicle that performs as impressively as it presents.",
      "price": 34500.0,
