      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next big adventure? I'm parting with this beauty, and it's in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved, runs super smooth, and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this car is a total joy to drive. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29900.0,
