    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 with its distinctive 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle body actuator service, ensuring the high-strung valvetrain remains robust. The chassis maintains its composure with EDC (Electronic Damper Control) and staggered forged wheels. While showing the minor aesthetic patina of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical integrity is excellent, offering a visceral analog experience that modern turbocharged units cannot replicate.",
